    "description": "<strong><i>Minima</i> is a chill, 2D platformer all about minimalism!</strong> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883020/extras/5acdd3da0be785b6fcf59613c6bb6375.webp?t=1714466263\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883020/extras/5acdd3da0be785b6fcf59613c6bb6375.poster.avif?t=1714466263\" class=\"bb_img\" width=613 height=160 /></picture></span><br>Immerse yourself in the laid-back ambience of simple graphics and a calming soundtrack in the world of <i>Minima!</i> Simplicity is key - only the most essential features of a platformer are present - and yet there is a high skill ceiling to master the game's tight controls. Precision and skill are vital in shaving seconds off of your runs, and you'll find new strategies and paths to take each time you play through a world.<br><br>This small indie project contains tonnes of passion and dedication from a single uni student who really doesn't know what he's doing with his life!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883020/extras/4562659727f6bbe69bf449c7de911380.webp?t=1714466263\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883020/extras/4562659727f6bbe69bf449c7de911380.poster.avif?t=1714466263\" class=\"bb_img\" width=613 height=160 /></picture></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Precise, snappy movement</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>500+ Unique Levels</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Accurate Timekeeping</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Online Leaderboards</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Chill Aesthetic</li></ul><br>I hope you enjoy!<br>- Icoso (the silliest game dev)",
